OMG! This is so funky. I remember attending the ALIF Concert at Edward theatre in Mumbai which was a part of "Poets Translating Poets" festival and the whole theatre was electrified by ALIF and gang. I really wished somebody could have released those songs which they performed that night because it was MAGICAL. I really hope ALIF relaunches all his amazing songs, i mean where were you all i have been looking up since forever! ***hand heart***

Also not forgetting to thank coke studio for this. Pls center more music and artists which mainstream audiences are not familiar with. Lots of love!
